-NJfoy3tyfJmZNzdlKBo.title: The Rise of Skywalker
-NJfoy3tyfJmZNzdlKBo.description: Among the charred irontrees of Mustafar, Kylo Ren strikes down anyone in his path as he makes his way to the ruins of Darth Vader's castle. He finds an ancient Sith artifact his grandfather once possessed: the Sith Wayfinder.
